<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000" size="5"><u>NCS Associate Mentor application updates</u></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b><font color="#cc0000"><br></font></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;">Hey&nbsp;<font face="arial">{!Contact.FirstName},&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font face="arial"><b><br></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><font face="arial">Here are a few <b>important </b>updates regarding your application to be an NCS Associate Mentor this summer.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><u><br></u></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><u>1) Additional assessments - &nbsp;please reserve your space!</u></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><ul><li>If you haven't yet attended an assessment, we are running just <b>two more next week</b>. You can find out more information and sign-up <b><a href="https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/associate-mentor-back-up-assessments-tickets-25860710080">HERE</a>.</b></li><li><b>PLEASE NOTE:</b> If you have already attended an assessment you will not be required to attend another.</li></ul></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b style="color: rgb(204, 0, 0);"><u>2) If you're going to be 18 or over before the end of August...</u></b></div><div style="text-align: left;"><ul><li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">You will need to have a Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) check. These can take several weeks to process so if you haven't started the application yet, <b><a href="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2016DBSinstructionsAMs.pdf">click here and get going</a>!</b></font></li><li><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">If you have already started your&nbsp;</span>application<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;but not yet completed it, make&nbsp;sure you finish it as soon as possible!</span></font></li><li>If you already completed your application, <b>well done!</b></li><li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b>Once you have&nbsp;received&nbsp;your DBS certificate, you will need to scan it and email it to samuel.hepher@the-challenge.org. You will then need to bring the original copy to your first day on the programme.</b></font></li></ul><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b><u>3) Wave allocation confirmations:</u></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><font face="arial">You will receive an email with confirmation of your allocated waves on <b>Friday 24th June</b>.</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b>Seven days</b>&nbsp;before your start date on each of your waves, you will receive an email with further information about locations, times and contacts.</font></li><li><font face="arial">After that, you will receive a call from your Assistant Programme Manager who will answer any questions you have ahead of your placement.</font></li></ul></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;">If you have any questions, please email samuel.hepher@the-challenge.org.&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;">See you soon!&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: left;"><b><br></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b>The Challenge Society</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</b></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>